            </h1></header><div class="ce-textpic ce-center ce-above"><div class="ce-bodytext"><ul><li><a href="/en/about-us/working-at-the-ipi?tracking-content-element=46118-7353&amp;cHash=a5289f4234f87840bf7dc1e163e48434" title="Working at the IPI" class="internal-link">Working at the IPI</a></li></ul><ul><li><a href="https://www.swissreg.ch/srclient/faces/jsp/start.jsp?tracking-content-element=46118-swissreg-ch" title="Trade mark, patent and design register" target="_blank" class="external-link" rel="noreferrer">Trade mark, patent and design register</a></li><li><a href="https://database.ipi.ch/database-client/search?tracking-content-element=46118-datenbank" title="Databases" target="_blank" class="external-link-new-window" rel="noreferrer">Databases</a></li></ul><ul><li><a href="/en/services/digital-resources/online-services?tracking-content-element=46118-7760&amp;cHash=7082d062f761e47eaf5eec95f4363a09" title="Online services" class="internal-link">Online services</a></li></ul><ul><li><a href="/en/services/training-and-courses?tracking-content-element=46118-7147&amp;cHash=5947884beb4f4d75fdfff38b64dd5cc8" title="Training and courses" class="internal-link">Training and courses</a></li></ul><ul><li><a href="/en/intellectual-property/counterfeiting-and-piracy?tracking-content-element=46118-7046&amp;cHash=d334d6f032b655f1c0b6a59035bc625d" title="Counterfeiting and piracy" class="internal-link">Counterfeiting and piracy</a></li><li><a href="/en/law-and-policy/national-ip-law/indications-of-source/swiss-indications-of-source/swissness?tracking-content-element=53789&amp;cHash=588edcac5951b5dd91cf58db92681914" title="Swissness" class="internal-link">Swissness</a></li></ul></div></div></div><!--DMAILER_SECTION_BOUNDARY_END--></div></div>



